voxfree (0.3.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * docs: present both ThinkPad (F9/F10/F11) and Standard (Super+Shift+R/M/K)
    shortcuts throughout all documentation and user-facing messages
  * docs: fix wrong Ctrl+Alt+S shortcut in voxfree-stop-all.sh comment
    (correct: Super+Shift+K)
  * new: voxfree --switch [thinkpad|standard] — switch keyboard shortcut
    layout after install without re-running full installer
  * new: lib/keyboard-layout.sh — shared helper for layout persistence
  * new: voxfree-switch.sh — layout switching implementation with multi-user
    session propagation (system mode iterates /run/user/*)
  * new: layout persistence — readloud.sh and speak-to-type.sh save the
    chosen layout to config so voxfree --switch knows the current state
  * runtime: all notify-send messages now show both shortcuts (e.g. "F9 or
    Super+Shift+R") so users always know their options
  * docs: update README.md, readloud.md, speak-to-type.md, architecture.md,
    building-blocks.md, CLAUDE.md with both layouts everywhere
  * CLI: voxfree --switch added to help text and voxfree wrapper

  -- VoxFree Project <voxfree@example.com>  Mon, 22 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0530

voxfree (0.1.1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * fix: F11 (voxfree-stop-all) now delegates to voxfree-dictate-stop when
    recording is active, so STT audio is transcribed instead of discarded
  * fix: speak-to-type.sh rewired to copy scripts from source files; previously
    it embedded and installed a stale toggle-based voxfree-dictate, breaking
    fresh installs of install.sh --all
  * fix: speak-to-type.sh now installs voxfree-dictate-stop and voxfree-stop-all,
    and writes correct dconf binding names (voxfree-readloud/dictate/stop-all)
  * docs: correct all stale script names (read-selection, speech-start/stop) in
    README.md, readloud.md, speak-to-type.md, docs/architecture.md,
    docs/building-blocks.md
  * docs: fix standard shortcuts throughout (Ctrl+Alt → Super+Shift)
  * docs: readloud.md — remove false clipboard fallback claim; add voxfree-stop-all
  * docs: architecture.md — correct F11 flow diagram, add F10/F11 shortcut flows,
    add voxfree-stop-all to file layout
  * docs: building-blocks.md — correct paste description to show smart paste
    (ctrl+shift+v for terminals, ctrl+v for apps)

 -- VoxFree Project <voxfree@example.com>  Sun, 12 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0530

voxfree (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release
  * ReadLoud: Text-to-Speech via Mycroft Mimic 3 (F9 toggle, voice selector)
  * SpeakToType: Speech-to-Text via Whisper base.en (F10 start, F11 stop+paste)
  * voxfree CLI: unified entry point (--install, --doctor, --voice, --uninstall)
  * voxfree-doctor: 36-point health checker
  * System and per-user install modes
  * .deb packaging with postinst configuration

 -- VoxFree Project <voxfree@example.com>  Sun, 12 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0530
